name: Warmup_Div05_Sub01
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD5S1.CPF,
GmailD5S1.NOME,
GmailD5S1.EMAIL,
GmailD5S1.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S1.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD5S1.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD5S1.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD5S1.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV05_SUB01 GmailD5S1
UNION
